- Good.

530
00:40:20,459 --> 00:40:22,419
Nicely done, Ernie.
Are you making this up?

531
00:40:22,586 --> 00:40:24,796
No, no.

532
00:40:27,842 --> 00:40:32,554
This is the Professor,
our new broker.

533
00:40:35,391 --> 00:40:36,975
Hi.

534
00:40:48,195 --> 00:40:51,197
You can handle a puny little bundle
like this, can't you?

535
00:40:51,365 --> 00:40:53,366
Yes, he can take care of it for us,
can't you?

536
00:40:53,534 --> 00:40:55,827
Oh, yeah, yeah, yeah.

537
00:40:55,995 --> 00:40:59,706
Hank, take the Professor
down to the tables.

538
00:40:59,874 --> 00:41:02,792
I understand you have
a very good system

